headline: Empire Provides E-Commerce Update
summary: Empire Company Limited ("Empire" or the "Company") (TSX: EMP.A) and its wholly-owned subsidiary, Sobeys Inc., today provided an e-commerce update focused on delivering immediate earnings improvement while expanding its successful third-party delivery partnerships. The actions contained in this update will allow the company to better serve the evolving needs of its online customers, particularly in the fastest-growing immediacy segment of e-commerce.
